1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Mamai expels Foma for failing to modern realities. Foma comes up with a plan for the return: get a teacher in a school where a child learns Mamai, wriggle to the child's confidence and thus recover in the eyes of Mamai. Foma arranged fizruk, met with the class where a child learns Mamai and with teachers, immediately falling in love with Tanya - the homeroom teacher of the class.

imdb.plot outline: The security director of a major Russian businessman is fired because of his old fashioned and violent work methods . The newly unemployed starts a job as a sports teacher in High school where the daughter of his ex boss is going, aiming to impress the girl and get his old job back.
